item.title: Add a new biobank to the Swedish COVID-19 Sample Collection database
item.description: The form below can be used to add a new biobank to the Swedish COVID-19 Sample Collection database which is part of the Swedish national COVID-19 data portal. All information provided in the form below will be displayed on the page of the biobank in the registry. Please fill in as many fields as possible so that the researchers have a good idea about what they can expect from the biobank.
